Moved e-Processos API data fetching from `BaseItemSerializer` to the content item layer. `EProcessosItem` now exposes a cached `data` property and a `fetch_data()` method, so serializers focus solely on transforming pre-loaded data. Added `EProcessosItem.from_data()` so collection serializers can wrap raw API items as content objects and serialize them through the standard `ISerializeToJson` machinery. @ericof
